  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## ⚠️ Redis Exporter Not Yet Configured\n\nThis dashboard requires **`redis_exporter`** (oliver006/redis_exporter) to be added to `docker-compose.yml` and scraped by Prometheus.\n\n**Required setup:**\n1. Add `redis_exporter` service to `docker-compose.yml` (image: `oliver006/redis_exporter:latest`, `REDIS_ADDR=redis://hts-redis:6379`)\n2. Add scrape target to `monitoring/prometheus.yml`: `job_name: redis`, target: `redis_exporter:9121`\n3. Restart Prometheus and the exporter\n\nOnce configured, panels below will populate with **Hit/Miss Ratio**, **Key Count**, **Memory Usage**, and **Connected Clients**.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Setup Required",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "last"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "redis_keyspace_hits_total / (redis_keyspace_hits_total + redis_keyspace_misses_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Hit Ratio",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "redis_keyspace_misses_total / (redis_keyspace_hits_total + redis_keyspace_misses_total)",
          "legendFormat": "Miss Ratio",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Hit / Miss Ratio [requires redis_exporter]",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": { "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(redis_keyspace_hits_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "Hits / s",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(redis_keyspace_misses_total[1m])",
          "legendFormat": "Misses / s",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Hits & Misses per Second [requires redis_exporter]",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "bytes"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": { "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "redis_memory_used_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Used Memory",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "redis_memory_max_bytes",
          "legendFormat": "Max Memory",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Memory Usage [requires redis_exporter]",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": { "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "redis_db_keys",
          "legendFormat": "Key Count",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "redis_connected_clients",
          "legendFormat": "Connected Clients",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Key Count & Connected Clients [requires redis_exporter]",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "10s",
